{"tid":1638960,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"World台出唔夠一日，已經變成玩膠既地方","createTime":"2019-10-08T13:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T13:12:27.000Z","uid":63822,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"519f0818d9184525b4798b953dd79fb0714b2560","tid":1638960,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"我唔知係5毛定真心膠搞事<br />\n<br />\n朝早都叫好地地，而家再望下，睇下幾多膠post<br />\n<br />\nWorld台係比大家將核彈新聞，文宣既英文版放上去比世界知<br />\n<br />\n什至比外國記者入黎問野<br />\n<br />\n好似轉微博支那人講911、教外國人開ac、解釋點解會有violence、日文韓文文宣之類既高質post，先係應該出現既野<br />\n<br />\n果堆「diu no chinese」，「薰一支一支一支咧點」係做乜鳩<br />\n<br />\n連登已經愈來愈唔可靠，但即使係咁都仲有好多記者會睇<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以唔好浪費左個新台？"},{"pid":"0df890bf9bf047a9bfdf3d3c6bf1cf9bc1fd8697","tid":1638960,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a22c8581878fd299058a4681bca89255c9a3e470","tid":1638960,"uid":236646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"好多on9"},{"pid":"7b7909501c8871b94ea3c98c6b934b74e435a08e","tid":1638960,"uid":183091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"緊急 希望有4000和理非幫手<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1638741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1638741</a>"},{"pid":"4aa72524a3dd2c50baba4f713086272f4fca9275","tid":1638960,"uid":78383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:10:34.000Z","msg":"但係呢個係連登文化<br />\n曾經都有外國人講過唔緊要，要keep番自己文化"},{"pid":"5d2e42a2c6bcff9a47e61ff572abe05337f10488","tid":1638960,"uid":147724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:10:54.000Z","msg":"根本上9成係膠post  有用post推唔到  喱度都係"},{"pid":"f0d8d80666e6ab22976051f9a3fa3e5a8e28a89f","tid":1638960,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:12:27.000Z","msg":"咁本身呢到係一個討論區<br />\n洗唔洗全撚部POST都關香港事先得呢?"}]}